🎬 7️⃣ EASY VIDEO CREATION PLAN (No-Face Workflow)

1️⃣ Find job/policy → Save link or PDF
2️⃣ Summarize: eligibility, apply date, website, benefit, how to apply
3️⃣ Make a 3–5 min script in Bengali
4️⃣ Screen record or slideshow (use CapCut / Canva)
5️⃣ Add your voiceover (clean, clear tone)
6️⃣ Add Bangla text & simple music
7️⃣ Create thumbnail:

Red/Yellow BG

Bold text (e.g. “নতুন চাকরি শুরু 🔥”)

Add photo of Modi / WBPSC logo/money bag icon


🧩 6️⃣ HOW TO TURN EACH UPDATE INTO A VIDEO

1. Find Circular or Policy (PDF or web post)

2. Read & Summarize Key Info:

Who can apply

Qualifications

Deadline

Apply the link or the steps

Script in 3 sections:

Hook (headline)

Explanation (details)

Application process or takeaway

Record Screen + Voice (use CapCut/OBS)

Could you add subtitles and a thumbnail?

Example workflow:
🕕 Morning – check 5 sites → choose 2 circulars
🕑 Noon – record 2 short videos
🕗 Evening – post 1 short + 1 long-form video



